    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“<strong>泳池清洁模拟器 </strong> 是一款类似 PowerWash Simulator 的清洁游戏，您可以在其中使用各种工具将肮脏的泳池变得闪闪发光。” 该游戏重现了清洁、擦洗和维护各种泳池的整个过程，从豪华的后院避风港到社区游泳馆。 扮演虚拟泳池清洁工的角色，接受挑战，将肮脏、被忽视的泳池变成闪闪发光的放松绿洲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>泳池清洁模拟器的主要特点</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>真实模拟</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/55bcfeb0d2d6f769f8fefdf91dd6dca4.poster.avif?t=1772062153\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/55bcfeb0d2d6f769f8fefdf91dd6dca4.webm?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/55bcfeb0d2d6f769f8fefdf91dd6dca4.mp4?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>沉浸在最真实的泳池清洁体验中，包括逼真的水物理原理和逼真的清洁工具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多样化的环境</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/6d52c0bdd0dccef34bbfd186d8aca888.poster.avif?t=1772062153\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/6d52c0bdd0dccef34bbfd186d8aca888.webm?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/6d52c0bdd0dccef34bbfd186d8aca888.mp4?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>遇到各种各样的泳池类型，每种泳池类型都带来独特的挑战。 从被郁郁葱葱的花园包围的住宅泳池到大型商业泳池，每一个场景都是一次新鲜的冒险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>动态天气</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/0a82f9c83985878cdb44ce845474e502.poster.avif?t=1772062153\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/0a82f9c83985878cdb44ce845474e502.webm?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/0a82f9c83985878cdb44ce845474e502.mp4?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>在不断变化的天气条件下（从烈日到小雨）处理清洁任务，增加额外的现实感和挑战。 （在 EA 发布后添加）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>升级及进度：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/9f713a1f4b0e8077d62d9581ac68730b.poster.avif?t=1772062153\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/9f713a1f4b0e8077d62d9581ac68730b.webm?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/9f713a1f4b0e8077d62d9581ac68730b.mp4?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>随着你的进步，解锁新的工具和设备，提高你作为一名出色的泳池清洁工的效率和效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>轻松的游戏玩法</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/2d9d46e38e593e41483cadaee3b2aec3.poster.avif?t=1772062153\" width=616 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/2d9d46e38e593e41483cadaee3b2aec3.webm?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/2d9d46e38e593e41483cadaee3b2aec3.mp4?t=1772062153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>当您目睹脏水池转变为原始静修处时，享受将冥想互动与成就感相结合的舒缓游戏体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抢先体验参与者将有独特的机会通过他们的反馈和建议来塑造泳池清洁模拟器的未来发展。 我们（Rubens Games）致力于与社区密切合作，完善游戏玩法，引入新功能，并确保最终版本的精美和令人愉快</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2165620/extras/458f1708827da7586c4d2243891a5bb9.avif?t=1772062153\" width=616 height=350 /></span></p>",
